title: OUR OFFICIAL BABY GENDER REVEAL!!!
author: THE WEISS LIFE
description:
OUR OFFICIAL BABY GENDER REVEAL!!!
The Weiss Family Official Gender Reveal! After having 5 girls we reveal the gender of baby # 6! Did you guess the gender right?! 

HUGE THANKS to our family and friends who made this day so special for us! We can’t wait to meet our new baby!

Don't forget to subscribe and turn on notifications! https://www.youtube.com/theweisslife
